donations.donation_comment: Thank you for standing up for freedom.

Support Canada Convoy! Thank you for your standing against tyranny, and fighting for freedom. Canada is leading the world of freedom because of you! I support this movement without hesitation, and will always!
You are an inspiration to Canada and the free world. I am so proud of you. You give me hope.
Love and respect to all truckers and supporters. You guys are the match that lit the flame of freedom in the hearts of Canadians and people of the world. We shall overcome!

GO TRUCKERS!! 
Shame on GoFundMe...I will NEVER donate to one of their groups again since they have shown that they can't be trusted.  
Thank you, GiveSendGo, for allowing your site to be used for the truckers. God bless all of you!!! 🙏🏼😇❤️🤗🙏🏼

Thank you so much for what you're doing!  You have my full support for this peaceful protest.  I hope that many more people will join you if needed and trust that your message of unity will shine through!
I stand with you. May God bless you, your families and everybody who is fighting for freedom. With all my love!
May God bless you stand for Liberty!

To all Canadian Truckers-
Admire you all!! In such a low temperatures far away from homes fighting for truth and our freedom. Never, never, never give up! You are example to the whole world. 

Viva Freedom!!! ❤️
